==English==
===Phrase===
'''[[lock]] and [[load]]'''
#{{US}} [[military]] [[command]] to put a [[weapon]]'s [[safety catch]] on, and load it with [[ammunition]] but it was load and lock (inserting a clip of ammunition into the rifle, loading the clip and locking the bolt forward)
#{{US}} Now, it's meaning has envolved and is commonly used to refer to preparation of any imminent event (in [[Boston legal]] series, Denny Crane use it in quite all episodes)